/**
 * lib/i18n/translations.ts
 * Hardcoded translations for STATIC UI text — keyed by the English source
 * string used in t("..."). These are served instantly with no API cost.
 *
 * Languages: hi, pa, mr, te, ta, bn, gu, kn, ml, od  (en = source, omitted).
 * Anything NOT in this map (dynamic AI output, live data) falls back to the
 * Sarvam translation layer in LanguageProvider.
 *
 * To add a string: wrap it in t("English") in the component, then add an entry
 * here. Missing entries simply render in English (or via the Sarvam fallback).
 */

